INSERT INTO `modx_site_content` VALUES ('58','document','text/html','Harish SIVASANKARAN','Harish SIVASANKARAN','','cl001','','1','0','0','57','0','','<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"9\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"content/images/cl001a.jpg\" /></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img width=\"32\" height=\"22\" src=\"content/images/flag/india.png\" /> <span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">India</span></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"bottom\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 140%;\">Harish SIVASANKARAN</span></strong></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Mechanical Engineering</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Studying at Asia&rsquo;s prestigious institute, The University of Tokyo is an　excellent and rewarding experience. The MEM program offers an excellent　platform for the international students to come and perform cutting edge　research and take courses in English without the knowledge of Japanese　proficiency. I whole heartedly recommend prospective students to utilize　this good program to the best of your advantage to study in The University　of Tokyo.</p>','1','5','1','1','0','1','1375173353','1','1506412709','0','0','0','1375173353','1','Harish SIVASANKARAN','0','0','0','0','0','0','1');
INSERT INTO `modx_site_content` VALUES ('59','document','text/html','Mike MUSIL','Mike MUSIL','','cl002','','1','0','0','57','0','','<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"9\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"content/images/cl002a.jpg\" /></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img width=\"22\" height=\"22\" src=\"content/images/flag/switzerland.png\" /><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"> Switzerland</span></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"bottom\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 140%;\">Mike MUSIL</span></strong></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Mechanical Engineering</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>I chose to apply at The University of Tokyo due to its great reputation and the opportunities students are given. Both the university and Japan are splendid places. Nevertheless, the bureaucracy can sometimes be burdensome. However, thanks to the help of the MEM office, it is made much easier for people not knowing Japanese or the culture to have a smooth start into the new life. I am very happy with the decision of applying at Todai through the MEM program and sincerely suggest everybody do the same who is interested in experiencing a new culture and conducting research at a top-tier university.</p>','1','5','2','1','0','1','1375173663','1','1506412696','0','0','0','1375173663','1','Mike MUSIL','0','0','0','0','0','0','1');
