INSERT INTO `modx_site_content` VALUES ('71','document','text/html','Nurul Ezailia ALIAS','Nurul Ezailia ALIAS','','1','','1','0','0','60','0','','<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"9\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"content/images/El001a.jpg\" /></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img width=\"32\" height=\"32\" src=\"content/images/flag/MY.png\" />&nbsp;Malaysia</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"bottom\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 140%;\">Nurul Ezailia ALIAS</span></strong></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Electrical Engineering and Information Systems</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>One of the things I really appreciate here is that every person behind MEM carries out their duties with full dedication in providing the best service to all international students. Each course is conducted using English, including using e-mail for notifications and so on. Furthermore, the examination system conducted here is very organized. On the other hand, as an international student, I was fascinated with Japanese culture. In fatigue studies here, I can learn a bit about Japanese culture through exciting activities organized by the MEM. I would like to congratulate all the students who will continue their studies here and for students who are interested, I advise not to miss this golden opportunity to study here because of its beauty cannot be expressed in words but you should feel yourself. I do not deny that it was difficult to qualify for further study here but if you worked hard, everything is possible. To be learned here, you must have a strong passion and discipline to realize your dreams. Final word from me, thorough preparation is very important in the examination and you must complete all the documents properly. I hope that all students who will study here will excel.</p>','1','5','3','1','0','1','1375680646','1','1506412755','0','0','0','1375680756','1','Nurul Ezailia ALIAS','0','0','0','0','0','0','1');
INSERT INTO `modx_site_content` VALUES ('72','document','text/html','Mohamad Samir A. EID','Mohamad Samir A. EID','','2','','1','0','0','60','0','','<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"9\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"content/images/El002a.jpg\" /></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img width=\"32\" height=\"32\" src=\"content/images/flag/EG.png\" /> Egypt</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"bottom\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 140%;\">Mohamad Samir A. EID</span></strong></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Electrical Engineering and Information Systems</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Like every Egyptian that I know, I have always been impressed by Japan\'s development and technology. Watching TV documentaries were not enough for me! I had to get myself in there and experience life in Japan! My father taught me to always aim to the top, and I couldn\'t find a higher ranked university in Japan, or the whole east, compared to the University of Tokyo. Thanks to the MEM International Graduate Program, and the dedication of its staff, my application went very smoothly. I was so lucky to receive such an opportunity and I heartily encourage all prospective students, especially Egyptian ones, to join this great institution.</p>','1','5','4','1','0','1','1375680791','1','1506412745','0','0','0','1375680859','1','Mohamad Samir A. EID','0','0','0','0','0','0','1');
