INSERT INTO `modx_site_content` VALUES ('74','document','text/html','Hao PANG','Hao PANG','','1','','1','0','0','73','0','','<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"9\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"content/images/Ma001a.jpg\" /></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img width=\"32\" height=\"32\" src=\"content/images/flag/CN.png\" /> China</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"bottom\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 140%;\">Hao PANG</span></strong></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Materials Engineering</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>I must say that MEM is a good choice. 1) Friends. There are students from 5 different departments and every year there are many events held by the MEM office, like parties and travels. By MEM I met people with different background and make lots of friends. 2) Support. Life in a foreign country is not so simple, but there&rsquo;s no need to be worried. During the Master course, I received many support from the MEM office.</p>','1','5','3','1','0','1','1375681074','1','1506412777','0','0','0','1375681210','1','Hao PANG','0','0','0','0','0','0','1');
INSERT INTO `modx_site_content` VALUES ('75','document','text/html','Changjoon LEE','Changjoon LEE','','2','','1','0','0','73','0','','<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"9\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"content/images/Ma002a.jpg\" /></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img width=\"32\" height=\"32\" src=\"content/images/flag/KR.png\" /> Korea</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"bottom\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 140%;\">Changjoon LEE</span></strong></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Materials Engineering</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Of course, the reason why I decided to study in the University of Tokyo was its fame in the field of steel research. However, since I sent the first e-mail to MEM office, I have found that international students can obtain more than just academic achievements in the University of Tokyo. MEM program has offered me many activities so that I could meet international friends from various fields/cultures and easily understand Japanese culture. If the virtues you are pursuing include communication skill and understanding diversity, MEM program will be the best choice for you.</p>','1','5','4','1','0','1','1375681074','1','1506412766','0','0','0','1375681273','1','Changjoon LEE','0','0','0','0','0','0','1');
