INSERT INTO `modx_site_content` VALUES ('87','document','text/html','Stephanie Liana SUTOKO','Stephanie Liana SUTOKO','','1','','0','0','0','86','0','','<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"9\"><img width=\"255\" height=\"340\" src=\"content/images/Ch001.JPG\" /></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img width=\"32\" height=\"32\" src=\"content/images/flag/ID.png\" /> Indonesia</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"bottom\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 140%;\">Stephanie Liana SUTOKO</span></strong></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Chemical System Engineering</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>We cannot question the popularity and quality of Engineering field in The University of Tokyo. Therefore, MEM International Graduate Program with 5 selectable Engineering Departments undoubtfully attracts students around the world who are triggered by these unlimited challenges and advantages for study abroad in Japan. It is my pleasure to be accepted in Chemical System Engineering Department through MEM International Graduate Program. Continuous follow-up and assistance both in intended application period and study life further make me feel this advanced opportunity. So, don&rsquo;t hesitate anymore, apply to your related department, join and taste the great experiences in here.</p>','1','5','3','1','0','1','1415682542','1','1437465314','0','0','0','0','0','Stephanie Liana SUTOKO','0','0','0','0','0','0','1');
