INSERT INTO `modx_site_content` VALUES ('223','document','text/html','Palar, Pramudita, Satria','Palar, Pramudita, Satria','','1','','1','0','0','222','0','','<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"8\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"content/images/campuslife/2015/image_cl_2015_aer_palar.jpg\" /></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><img width=\"32\" height=\"32\" src=\"content/images/flag/ID.png\" />&nbsp;Indonesia</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 140%;\"><strong>Palar, Pramudita, Satria</strong></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Aeronautics and Astronautics</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>As for my background, I did my Ph.D. at The University of Tokyo under the supervision of Professor Takeshi Tsuchiya in the field of aerospace design. To be exact, I was developing a method to accelerate engineering design optimization process that combines a so-called artificial evolution and function approximation technique. Moreover, I was also working on the development of uncertainty quantification methodology, which is a subject undergoing intense study&nbsp; in science and engineering right now.</p>\n<p>Studying at the University of Tokyo is probably one of the best experiences that I&rsquo;ve ever had in life. The experience is totally life-changing and also broadens my knowledge and experience: the research atmosphere, the vibrant city, and superb research facilities. During my Ph.D., I also had an opportunity to become a visiting researcher at University of Cambridge (UK) to work in collaboration with Dr. Geoffrey Thomas Parks during which I was fully supported by my Professor at Tokyo morally and financially. Constant interactions with worldly renowned Professors are truly a rare experience, and you could exactly have that at the University of Tokyo! The IME staffs were also very helpful while still being very cheerful, even I sometimes shared my university life problems with them.</p>\n<p>One thing that is really worth mentioning is that education at the University of Tokyo is really affordable compared to its western counterparts.&nbsp; On top of that, the chance to receive a scholarship is also higher relative to other developed countries, that is, you can study at University of Tokyo by using a scholarship support from either the Japanese government, private companies, or private/national organizations (I received my scholarship from Japan International Cooperation Agency), or if you have a highly supportive professor, even he/she could support you with the lab&rsquo;s funding!</p>\n<p>Now if you are searching for a university that could provide you a top engineering and science education with a top-notch research quality; stop right there, you already found the best one for you: University of Tokyo. Especially if you want to go for engineering studies, joining IME might be&nbsp; the best path for you. To all future engineers, scientists, researchers, and entrepreneurs (especially my Indonesian fellow): trust me, joining University of Tokyo will be one of the best experiences that you will ever have in life. It will boost your international competitiveness, connections, and skills; surely they would be highly beneficial for your future career.</p>','1','5','1','1','0','1','1517902918','1','1517903076','0','0','0','1517902918','1','Palar, Pramudita, Satria','0','0','0','0','1','0','0');
INSERT INTO `modx_site_content` VALUES ('224','document','text/html','Amir Reuveny','Amir Reuveny','','3','','1','0','0','209','0','','<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"8\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"content/images/campuslife/2015/image_cl_2015_ele_amir.jpg\" /></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><img width=\"32\" height=\"32\" src=\"content/images/flag/IL.png\" /> Israel</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong><span style=\"font-size: 140%;\">Amir Reuveny</span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Electrical Engineering and Information Systems</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>The IME program at the University of Tokyo provides a unique opportunity to study in one of the leading institutions in the world and having an unforgettable cultural experience! The staff at IME is wonderful and caring, facilitating the administrative aspects of the relocation and organizing fun international gatherings and social events. I had the opportunity to work with the best experts developing organic ultra-flexible electronics, learning new techniques and methodologies, and being recognized internationally for our achievements. During the studies I&rsquo;ve made lifetime friendships with lab members and international colleagues from all around the globe, studied a new language, traveled in beautiful world heritage sites and discovered an amazing culture. Highly recommended!</p>','1','5','3','1','0','1','1519714528','1','1519714528','0','0','0','1519714528','1','Amir Reuveny','0','0','0','0','1','0','1');
